item.title: I Need Help Makeing A Client (sorry if its in wrong board)
item.dc:creator: @frogtamer101 frogtamer101
item.description:
@frogtamer101 wrote:

To make a total Client from scratch is a little much if you dont even know how to get to the right section of the forums, no offence. You should start by going to the client hacking section or the search bar and find a blank or bare client to build upon. From there you can edit files in there to your liking and make your own. Be sure to give credit to the original person you downloaded it from.

Good Luck!
